Solution: (HASH SET) : T.C. - O(N), S.C. - O(N)

Approach: The linkedlist will repeat values for sure, we have to catch the value that repaeats first so
used set(). As soon as the first element repeats, it returns True

class Solution:
    def hasCycle(self, head: Optional[ListNode]) -> bool:
        seen = set()
        curr = head

        while curr:
            if curr in seen:
                return True
            seen.add(curr)
            curr = curr.next
        return False
